    ns1:otherInformation """This subject will be taught in English.
In this subject no Sustainable Development Goal (ODS) is directly worked upon. Nevertheless, as part of a public university, we declare our full involvement with ODS 4: Ensure inclusive and equitable quality education and promote lifelong learning opportunities for all."""@es ;
    ns1:periodEndingMonth "Enero"@es ;
    ns1:periodStartingMonth "Septiembre"@es ;
    ns1:teachingPeriod "2025-26" ;
    ns1:teachingPeriodMonths "Septiembre-Enero"@es ;
